00:50.290 --> 00:51.750
Rick: Graffiti here in grandview?

00:51.750 --> 00:52.830
Are you sure there was graffiti?

00:52.830 --> 00:54.500
I mean,was the handwriting nice,at least?

00:54.500 --> 00:55.570
Ok,this isn't funny,

00:55.570 --> 00:57.470
and we're not just talking about some random tagger.

00:57.470 --> 00:58.490
It was meant for me.

00:58.490 --> 00:59.400
Well,I wouldn't worry about it.

00:59.400 --> 01:00.970
It's probably some stupid prank,some kids.

01:00.970 --> 01:02.730
Why would they write that?

01:02.730 --> 01:04.930
All right,have you been on and shame the devil lately?

01:04.930 --> 01:07.520
-What?
-Justin yates' obnoxious blog?

01:07.520 --> 01:08.230
No.

01:08.230 --> 01:12.890
Well,there's been some chatter lately,a bunch of posts,about you.

01:13.910 --> 01:18.280
A person of interest in grandview who claims to have more than a passing acquaintance with the dead.

01:18.280 --> 01:21.030
I've heard about a store in town where really weird stuff happens.

01:21.030 --> 01:22.420
I can't believe this.

01:22.420 --> 01:23.930
It's like he's trying to out me.

01:23.930 --> 01:25.160
How long has this been happening?

01:25.160 --> 01:26.180
I don't know,a week.

01:26.180 --> 01:27.660
But don't even pay attention to it.

01:27.660 --> 01:28.940
You should see what they write about me.

01:28.940 --> 01:30.840
He knows things,thanks to your careful

01:30.840 --> 01:32.650
and thorough notes that you let him steal,

01:32.650 --> 01:34.720
he knows everything about me.

01:34.720 --> 01:37.740
Do you have any idea what my life is going to be like if this gets out?

01:37.740 --> 01:38.820
I didn't let him steal my notes.

01:38.820 --> 01:40.580
He stole my notes 'cause he's clever,he's cunning.

01:40.580 --> 01:42.210
He lives on campus,right?

01:42.210 --> 01:44.050
Take me to him.

01:45.730 --> 01:48.170
You put this out there,justin.

01:48.170 --> 01:49.910
I thought you were going to keep my secret.

01:49.910 --> 01:51.350
Why are you trying to hurt me?

01:51.350 --> 01:53.660
I'm not trying to hurt anybody.

01:53.660 --> 01:55.450
People come to my blog for the truth.

01:55.450 --> 01:56.980
Oh,yeah,'cause you're all about the truth.

01:56.980 --> 01:59.040
Look,this is a bad time,ok?

01:59.040 --> 02:00.420
Hey,justin,this might be a good time to tell you

02:00.420 --> 02:04.020
about a fascinating new invention called the hanger.

02:04.020 --> 02:06.260
Besides,according to the professor's notes,

02:06.260 --> 02:07.910
you've helped a lot of people.

02:07.910 --> 02:09.479
You've affected a lot of people.

02:09.479 --> 02:11.290
I mean,how long do you expect to keep this a secret?

02:11.290 --> 02:14.260
Exactly,justin,I have helped a lot of people.

02:14.260 --> 02:17.520
And if this gets out,my life is going to be turned upside down.

02:17.520 --> 02:20.030
Rick: Interesting choice of words.

02:20.030 --> 02:22.780
Hey,give that to me.

02:25.770 --> 02:29.170
Look,I came to you a long time ago with a lot of questions,

02:29.170 --> 02:31.500
and you gave me nothing,and now you want my help?

02:31.500 --> 02:32.570
I don't want anything from you.

02:32.570 --> 02:35.120
I just want to be left alone.

02:35.240 --> 02:38.160
That may not be possible.

